cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.CR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the performance analysis of cooperative schemes in a wireless network, which involves information transmission and processing. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on the performance evaluation and optimization of relaying schemes in a wireless network, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the analysis and optimization of a communication system, which involves control and feedback mechanisms. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper involves the transmission and processing of multimedia data in a wireless network, which falls under the scope of multimedia. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper involves the analysis of the error probability in a wireless network, which is relevant to the security and reliability of the communication system.
